"Return the vector of the affine combination.

Returns
-------
out : :class:`~openturns.Point`
    The constant term

Examples
--------
>>> import openturns as ot
>>> distribution = ot.RandomMixture([ot.Uniform(-1.0, 1.0), ot.Uniform(-1.0, 1.0)])
>>> # Constant term is 0
>>> cst = distribution.getConstant()
>>> print(cst)
[0]"

